headline: Ross Stores (ROST): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q3 Earnings?
summary: Ross Stores trades at $153.80 per share and has stayed right on track with the overall market, gaining 5.3% over the last six months. At the same time, the S&P 500 has returned 9.7%.

headline: World shares mixed as 2024 trading winds down
summary: European and Asian shares were mixed Friday in thin year-end trading, with European markets moving in narrow ranges as they reopened after Christmas holidays.
